<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="184" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[136,1451,734,977]" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">
<bibRefCitation author="Martius, C. F. P. V." box="[136,304,734,760]" pageId="4" pageNumber="184" pagination="1 - 112" refId="ref7887" refString="Martius, C. F. P. V. (1841) Beiblatter zur Flora oder Botanische Zeitung. Flora oder Botanische Zeitung: welche Recensionen, Abhandlungen, Aufsatze, Neuigkeiten und Nachrichten, die Botanik betreffend, enthalt 24 (2, Beiblatt II): 1 - 112." type="book chapter" year="1841">Martius (1841)</bibRefCitation>
reported his collection number 
<quantity box="[662,733,734,761]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.32842" pageId="4" pageNumber="184" unit="in" value="523.0">523 in</quantity>
the protologue, but 
<bibRefCitation author="Cunha, M. C. S." box="[959,1114,734,761]" pageId="4" pageNumber="184" pagination="5 - 41" refId="ref7419" refString="Cunha, M. C. S. (1985) Revisao das especies do genero Luehea Willd. (Tiliaceae), ocorrentes no estado do Rio de Janeiro. Sellowia, Anais Botanicos do Herbario Barbosa Rodrigues 37: 5 - 41." type="journal article" year="1985">
<collectingCountry box="[959,1032,734,760]" name="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">Cunha</collectingCountry>
(1985)
</bibRefCitation>
cited collection 
<emphasis box="[1300,1451,734,760]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">Luschnath 24</emphasis>
(M) as the ‘holotype’, but without having seen it. However, this specimen is not original material for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1841" box="[1287,1451,770,796]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="184" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ochrophylla">
<emphasis box="[1287,1451,770,796]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">L. ochrophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
because it was not mentioned in the protologue. The original specimen is 
<emphasis box="[969,1114,806,832]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">Martius 523,</emphasis>
part of the collection 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">
“Martii Herbar Florae 
<collectingCountry box="[307,381,842,868]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">Brasil</collectingCountry>
”
</emphasis>
, and mostly preserved in M, but with duplicates in several other herbaria. We designated herein 
<emphasis box="[136,274,878,904]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">Martius 523</emphasis>
(L2352817) as the 
<typeStatus box="[497,600,878,904]" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">lectotype</typeStatus>
in accordance with Art. 9.3 of the ICN because it is the most complete and best-preserved specimen congruent with the protologue’s description. Based on the type materials, the application of the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1841" box="[245,408,950,976]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="4" pageNumber="184" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ochrophylla">
<emphasis box="[245,408,950,976]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">L. ochrophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is confirmed as an accepted species, as proposed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cunha, M. C. S." box="[1002,1161,950,977]" pageId="4" pageNumber="184" pagination="5 - 41" refId="ref7419" refString="Cunha, M. C. S. (1985) Revisao das especies do genero Luehea Willd. (Tiliaceae), ocorrentes no estado do Rio de Janeiro. Sellowia, Anais Botanicos do Herbario Barbosa Rodrigues 37: 5 - 41." type="journal article" year="1985">
<collectingCountry box="[1002,1075,950,976]" name="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" pageId="4" pageNumber="184">Cunha</collectingCountry>
(1985)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
